{
  "stem": "11552.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The ghetto is going to be canceled, and the people can go to one place I know of-- to Kopyczynce, to the ghetto of Kopyczynce.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I imagine there must have been another place, what I wasn't aware of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my mother and my little brother, and I went to the ghetto of Kopyczynce.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any particular action?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we had-- we had several actions during that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One, the first-- our first hiding place was in the wall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a stone wall that my brother built.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in order to close it, my brother had to stand there and actually hold the stone from the opening.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- And they were hitting the wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't hit that particular place where the opening was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, the-- the thing I want to-- would like to share with you is my-- my very great disappointment, of course, that we children couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But what happened is it was still the beginning, in 1941, when the Christian children went back to school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I gathered my Jewish friends, and I decided that I'm going to make a statement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we all walked into our classroom and sat in our seats.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when the teacher walked in and she saw us there, she got pale to her face.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she said, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, because you are not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You all have to leave the classroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I loved my teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to give her any problems.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on the way back, I thought there must be some way I could continue learning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really loved learning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a tree growing very close to the window of our classroom.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
